    "body": "Gotcha. Yeah the agents have m2c available, but realizing I did not force it to start there. Will ensure that is forced as first step in flow, and add in logic on the verifier to reject common slop patterns (raw offset pointer arithmetic, NOT_IMPLEMENTED stubs, and C99 loop-variable declarations) before accepting writes.\r\n\r\nAppreciate this feedback! Will hop into the discord and try and also integrate other ideas I see in there to avoid generating more low quality work. Thanks for the review",
